JAGX Stocks tend to lag the market after a reverse split Thats not surprising if a reverse split signals that management thinks the stock will continue to decline However its worth repeating A reverse split is an effect of poor performance not a cause The stock often has already been on a long downtrend and the reverse split is just a gimmick to keep the stock on the exchange or in investors hands not a real operational repair of the business
